      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW LIAM (8) missed the frame last time, finishing 6th (26.05) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Warragul. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including two wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has ability and looks hard to stop. PAW KRAMER (6) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (23.20) behind Moonlight Grand at Horsham. Expecting another good run. BANJO ONE STRING (1) missed the frame two back but wound up strongly last time, finishing on late when second (24.84) in a Free For All at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to feature. DR. LEVIATE (3) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
